ry\nresult, we obtain the $p$-harmonic index and nullity of $\\varphi$. In the final\nsection we compare our general results with those which can be deduced from the\nstudy of the equivariant second variation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jan 2022 16:04:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-26"}
