{B}(x))$ are equivalent, with the\n$\\{\\vec{\\mathcal{E}}(x),\\vec{\\mathcal{B}}(x)\\}$ description satisfying the\nextended Hertz-form Maxwell's equations in the low speed approximation. The\nsolution of (extended) Hertz-form Maxwell's equations describe the traveling\nwave form electromagnetic field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jan 2022 10:36:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Jan 2022 13:48:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 31 Jan 2022 11:02:41 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 24 Mar 2022 19:22:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-28"}
