ound detection. A\nfirst module with a mass of at least 500 kg may be operating as early as 2026\nat the LSC.\n  In this manuscript, recent results obtained with the NEXT-White detector will\nbe presented, as well as the NEXT-100 construction status and on the prospects\nof future NEXT detectors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jan 2022 12:49:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
