 tested platforms, achieving an average speedup of 3.9$\\times$\n(7.3$\\times$ on CPUs and 2.8$\\times$ on GPUs) and maximum speedup of\n10.6$\\times$ on Intel UHD P630 GPU.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jan 2022 14:18:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-27"}
